 Masolo na bango mazalaki mpo koluka lolenge bikolo mibale bakoki kokolisa boyokani na bango.
Na bobimi waye, ambassadeur ya Ameriki, Todd Haskell alalaki ete Ameriki ekopesa maboko na ekolo Congo-Brazzaville na nzela ya AGOA (African growth opportunities Act) mobeko moye mopesa nzela na mboka nzike kosala mobongo na Etats-Unis.